                            <comment id="12420785" author="bayard" created="Thu, 13 Jul 2006 10:30:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hard to test (anyone got an AIX?) but we signed up for that by having a method that wasn&apos;t platform independent.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12425446" author="grimsell" created="Thu, 3 Aug 2006 06:59:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;HP-UX has the same issue as AIX. The attached file contains a fix where the method freeSpaceUnix takes a boolean posix which indicates whether to add the -P flag or not. For HP-UX and AIX psix arg is set to true.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12430638" author="scolebourne" created="Fri, 25 Aug 2006 21:44:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Change made in rv436964&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Please retest using nighly build at &lt;a href=&quot;http://people.apache.org/builds/jakarta-commons/nightly/commons-io/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://people.apache.org/builds/jakarta-commons/nightly/commons-io/&lt;/a&gt; from the 26thAug&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We&apos;d appreciate feedback before releasing the code.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
